| mstats rate_avg("ifcounters.in_octets") as "in_rate" WHERE index="mertics_data" AND telegraf_tag="gnmi" AND (name="GigabitEthernet0/0/0/0" OR name="GigabitEthernet0/0/0/1" OR name="GigabitEthernet0/0/0/2") AND source="xr-1" span=1m BY name | eval now = now() | where _time > (now - 120) | stats sum(in_rate) as "Total_Inbound_Rate"
